    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-01-25T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-01-25T19:00:00-05:00" n="252"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d252">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 657.119/273a</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Norway</hi> (<persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_SAG1"
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schmedeman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-01-25T19:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 25, 1918—7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>216. We are giving to the press within next few days full schedule of commodities
                    and substance of our proposal of December 20, containing, however, no intimation
                    of that which has been offered or proposed to the United States by Norway.<note
                        n="1" xml:id="d252fn1">For the War Trade Board’s statement, see <hi
                            rend="italic">The Official Bulletin</hi>, Washington, Jan. 28, 1918
                        (vol. 2, No. 219), pp. 13 and 15–16.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_PFL1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
